36
00:03:31,959 --> 00:03:37,730
However, some bias-reduction success has been obtained by getting people to think through

37
00:03:37,730 --> 00:03:43,760
what’s known as “counterfactuals” – that is, all the other ways that events 

38
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:44,609
could have played out.

39
00:03:44,609 --> 00:03:50,249
So, in principle, in our demonstration we might first ask you to imagine that Fox was

40
00:03:50,249 --> 00:03:55,719
