41
00:03:55,719 --> 00:04:02,719
that Fox was found not guilty, and consider reasons why this might occur. We’d predict 

42
00:04:03,469 --> 00:04:07,579
that this ought to reduce the hindsight bias.

43
00:04:07,579 --> 00:04:11,980
In everyday life, you might find it generally useful to think through the “counterfactuals”

44
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:18,209
– the alternative hypotheses – whenever you need to make an important judgement. 

45
